    <item>
      <title>Github Pages, Hugo si Cloudflare</title>
      <link>https://blog.pakithecat.eu/ro/posts/2025/githubpages-cloudflare/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Jul 2025 12:18:07 +0300</pubDate>
      <guid>https://blog.pakithecat.eu/ro/posts/2025/githubpages-cloudflare/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;cum-sa-rutezi-site-ul-tau-github-pages-prin-cloudflare-pe-un-subdomeniu&#34;&gt;Cum sa rutezi site-ul tau GitHub Pages prin Cloudflare pe un subdomeniu&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ai un site gazduit pe &lt;strong&gt;GitHub Pages&lt;/strong&gt;, de genul &lt;code&gt;https://usergithub.github.io/my-blog/&lt;/code&gt;, si vrei sa-l accesezi printr-un &lt;strong&gt;subdomeniu personalizat&lt;/strong&gt; (ex: &lt;code&gt;blog.domeniultau.ro&lt;/code&gt;) folosind &lt;strong&gt;Cloudflare&lt;/strong&gt;?
Este o modalitate excelenta de a-ti imbunatati performanta, securitatea si de a avea un URL mai curat. Iata cum poti face asta, pas cu pas!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;pasul-1-pregateste-domeniul-tau-in-cloudflare&#34;&gt;Pasul 1: Pregateste domeniul tau in Cloudflare&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Daca nu ai facut deja acest pas esential, va trebui sa iti &lt;strong&gt;adaugi domeniul principal&lt;/strong&gt; (cum ar fi &lt;code&gt;domeniultau.ro&lt;/code&gt;) in Cloudflare. Procesul implica schimbarea serverelor de nume ale domeniului la cele oferite de Cloudflare &lt;a href=&#34;https://developers.cloudflare.com/dns/zone-setups/full-setup/setup/&#34;&gt;(see docs)&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OCI - Atașarea si montarea unui volum bloc</title>
      <link>https://blog.pakithecat.eu/ro/posts/2025/oci-mount-block-volume/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Feb 2025 16:27:00 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://blog.pakithecat.eu/ro/posts/2025/oci-mount-block-volume/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Urmeaza &lt;a href=&#34;https://docs.oracle.com/en-us/iaas/Content/Block/Tasks/connectingtoavolume_topic-Connecting_to_iSCSIAttached_Volumes.htm&#34;&gt;ghidul&lt;/a&gt; Oracle pentru a atasa volumul nou creat, apoi executa pasii urmatori:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;identifica-noul-disc-de-exemplu-devsdb-&#34;&gt;Identifica noul disc (de exemplu, &lt;code&gt;/dev/sdb&lt;/code&gt; )&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;sudo fdisk -l
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h4 id=&#34;creaza-o-partitie-daca-este-necesar&#34;&gt;Creaza o partitie (daca este necesar)&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;sudo fdisk /dev/sdb
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apasa &lt;code&gt;n&lt;/code&gt; pentru a crea o noua partitie.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Alege tipul partitiei (&lt;code&gt;p&lt;/code&gt; pentru primara)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Selecteaza valorile implicite sau specifica o dimensiune.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apasa &lt;code&gt;w&lt;/code&gt; pentru a salva modificarile.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;formateaza-partitia&#34;&gt;Formateaza partitia&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;sudo mkfs.ext4 /dev/sdb1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h4 id=&#34;creaza-un-punct-de-montare&#34;&gt;Creaza un punct de montare&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;sudo mkdir -p /mnt/mydrive
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h4 id=&#34;monteaza-discul&#34;&gt;Monteaza discul&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;sudo mount /dev/sdb1 /mnt/mydrive
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h4 id=&#34;montare-automata-la-pornire&#34;&gt;Montare automata la pornire&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Obtine UUID-ul partitiei&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;sudo blkid /dev/sdb1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Editeaza fisierul &lt;code&gt;/etc/fstab&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;sudo nano /etc/fstab
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adauga linia de mai jos la sfarsit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;UUID&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;your-uuid&amp;gt;  /mnt/mydrive  ext4  defaults,noatime,_netdev  &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Salveaza fisierul&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Cum sa folosesti GPG pentru a cripta/decripta fisiere</title>
      <link>https://blog.pakithecat.eu/ro/posts/2025/gpg/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 15:24:43 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://blog.pakithecat.eu/ro/posts/2025/gpg/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;GnuPG foloseste criptografia cu chei publice astfel incat utilizatorii sa poata comunica in siguranta. Intr-un sistem cu chei publice, fiecare utilizator are o pereche de chei formata dintr-o cheie privata si o cheie publica. Cheia privata a unui utilizator este pastrata secreta si nu trebuie dezvaluita niciodata. Cheia publica poate fi oferita oricui doreste utilizatorul sa comunice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;instalare-si-generare-pereche-de-chei&#34;&gt;Instalare si generare pereche de chei&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;instalare pe Debian / Ubuntu&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;sudo apt-get install gnupg
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;generarea unei perechi de chei&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;vom folosi ca exemplu adrese de email de genul &lt;code&gt;johndoe@example.com&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;gpg --full-generate-key
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;schimbul-de-chei-export--import&#34;&gt;Schimbul de chei (export / import)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;exportul unei chei public in format binar&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;gpg --output johndoe.gpg --export johndoe@example.com
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;sau ACII&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;gpg --armor --output johndoe.gpg.pub --export johndoe@example.com
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;importul unei chei publice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;gpg --import janedoe.gpg
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;gpg --list-keys
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;validarea unei chei publice importate (manual, daca este cazul)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;gpg --edit-key blake@cyb.org
#afiseaza amprenta
fpr 
#semneaza cheia
sign
#verifica cheia
check
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;criptarea-si-decriptarea-documentelor-pentru-un-anumit-destinatar&#34;&gt;Criptarea si decriptarea documentelor (pentru un anumit destinatar)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;criptare&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;gpg --output doc.gpg --encrypt --recipient janedoe@example.com doc.txt
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;decriptare&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;gpg --output doc-dec.txt --decrypt doc.gpg
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>WinSCP - sudo dupa autentificare</title>
      <link>https://blog.pakithecat.eu/ro/posts/2025/first/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 10:55:00 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://blog.pakithecat.eu/ro/posts/2025/first/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Recent, a trebuit sa incarc cateva foldere pe un server Linux (Oracle Cloud), dar permisiunile utilizatorului pe care le aveam nu imi permiteau sa creez folderele necesare. In cautarea unei solutii, am dat peste aceasta posibilitate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In unele cazuri (cu servere Unix/Linux), poti folosi comanda &lt;code&gt;sudo&lt;/code&gt; imediat dupa autentificare pentru a schimba utilizatorul, inainte ca sesiunea de transfer de fisiere sa inceapa.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Protocoalele &lt;em&gt;SFTP&lt;/em&gt; si &lt;em&gt;SCP&lt;/em&gt; permit acest lucru, dar metoda efectiva depinde de platforma.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
